{"tid":2499411,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"[樂理]和弦旋律分析 － 入黎劑低你想執既歌","createTime":"2021-04-22T00:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T23:23:20.000Z","uid":56674,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf71a23786a2d2b2b614939c140ff98baaea8bba","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:59:15.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係蘭調人，我係一個全職既結他老師，有任何野想問我可以透過telegram搵到我： <a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8036fc24\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a><br />\n<br />\n下面有義教post詳情可以睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於上一個post大家反應冷淡，寫得太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次開新post接受大家挑戰，幫大家執大家聽唔到／解唔明既chord progression。大家可以：<br />\n1. 劑低你地想我幫手聽既youtube link／其他source<br />\n2. 講低秒數，由邊度至邊度<br />\n3. 你暫時聽到／網上睇到既版本係點<br />\n<br />\n盡可能細佬我可以upload 番結他 chord chart，同拍段好短既youtube彈一次出黎show一次點彈。多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419c3557c02d534a3916c96a9b295258d0f3c941","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"期間限定<br />\n細佬我將會再次回饋連登，舉行每星期一至兩次的<span class=\"gold\"><strong>義教</strong></span>連登巴絲結他課堂。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n－適合新手／卡樽頸已久的連登結他巴絲<br />\n－電／木結他皆可<br />\n－任何風格（我識答既就答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n－因為以前做過幾次都有放飛機既人，所以每星期只有固定兩日可選（響細佬我平時教班既節數之間或之後）<br />\n－每人可以黎最多1次<br />\n－響葵興，我的教室<br />\n－土地問題，所以每次最多1對1或1對2<br />\n－自攜結他同彈過既譜／notes<br />\n－由即日起可以報名，完結時間另行通知<br />\n－時段：<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>星期三－6pm 7pm 8pm<br />\n星期六－3pm 4pm<br />\n星期日－10am 11am</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概會講既內容：<br />\n1. 流行結他（即係普通彈唱）－中階<br />\n－點樣可以無perfect pitch，用結他指板可以搵到一首歌既key<br />\n－點樣可以執到譜／chord／識得分網上簡譜執得岩唔岩<br />\n－點樣可以彈得似原本果首歌多一啲<br />\n－掃法／勾法變化<br />\n－結他編曲編chord<br />\n－知道歌係點寫出黎<br />\n－更多內容未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n2. Blues（電結他soloing）<br />\n－基本shuffle blues soloing方法：用arpeggios/chord tone，而非pentatonics<br />\n－基本 12 bar blues comping，minor blues同shuffle blues<br />\n－大師風格剖析簡介，主要3 Kings，Jimi，Clapton，SRV<br />\n－Playing sometimes outside，如何更改12-bar blues progression內的chord產生新的outside soloing line<br />\n－standard licks and runs in both major/minor pentatonic scale<br />\n－點樣調教amp既EQ／結他上的pot value／用咩effect去拎到一個標準tone<br />\n<br />\n3. Jazz Guitar<br />\n－練習Routine：於固定把位上將chord shapes/arpeggios 沿circle of Vth彈奏<br />\n－Comping：隨住fake book上的chord將一隻jazz standard完整comp出（用chord fragment同特定rhythm有脈絡地一個接一個彈出）<br />\n－分析chord progression in any jazz standards：響任何的standard上solo或comp前都必需要做的一步<br />\n－正確基本3大modes：Ionian，Dorian，Mixolydian<br />\n－ii - V - I 於 bebop/jazz guitar soloing的標準彈奏方法／chord擺法<br />\n－太多未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以直接聯絡我：<a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8036fc24\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a>"},{"pid":"65e1bba62ba6897e4b3bfe4258f29007cc3093a1","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"你好，想請教一首舊歌《遇見》孫燕姿<br />\n想問中間一段間奏(1&rsquo;43&rdquo;開始嗰段，我估應該8個chord)係咩chord同點解?（係咪modal interchange?)<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"085b93e90306e68b4e050e13b4257c5902321b86","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e1bba62ba6897e4b3bfe4258f29007cc3093a1","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"你好，想請教一首舊歌《遇見》孫燕姿<br />\n想問中間一段間奏(1&rsquo;43&rdquo;開始嗰段，我估應該8個chord)係咩chord同點解?（係咪modal interchange?)<br />\nThanks"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:47:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩聽左，係G# - C#m6，形狀後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係modal interchange，I - iv<br />\n<br />\n（左至右係由粗至幼）<br />\n大概係 G# : x 11 13 13 13 11<br />\nC#m6 : 9 x 11 9 11 x"},{"pid":"db8fed4459c0c39917b73b7d55ddaa47ef845127","tid":2499411,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"我反而想學下自己執<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c7ed4a5d9c9292315f1b35fbb6d6e8cbcd665b","tid":2499411,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"想知道點樣練耳仔, 自己音感好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底應該係用d app, 直接聽兩個單音之間既音程去練,<br />\n定係直接聽歌?<br />\n有時都聽到最高同bassline, 但中間個d完全聽唔到"},{"pid":"31aea876404c2db320e4e76d3a8e0e7b52f2c216","tid":2499411,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"要去到咩程度先聽到哂呢首既chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O06BmbcLL9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO06BmbcLL9E&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9e2b0a2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O06BmbcLL9E</a>"},{"pid":"ce1b16d9dca4d0ddf1759927d8792b069cb74cde","tid":2499411,"uid":236608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢想請教下<br />\n有人話作曲最好寫chord先？想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係寫咗melody再配chord反而更match咩？"},{"pid":"ae8edc6799107d6b99e3d2c00bbd4c5ba6f4f7d9","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085b93e90306e68b4e050e13b4257c5902321b86","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e1bba62ba6897e4b3bfe4258f29007cc3093a1","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"你好，想請教一首舊歌《遇見》孫燕姿<br />\n想問中間一段間奏(1&rsquo;43&rdquo;開始嗰段，我估應該8個chord)係咩chord同點解?（係咪modal interchang