replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得由一個major key轉去佢parallel minor key,似轉mode多過轉調，成件事沉晒，跟住轉返parallel major,件事又升番起晒。<br />\n<br />\n印象中AGA首Tonight 都係咁，不過倒轉：段verse先用B minor key, 製造柔情含蓄感覺，去到chorus就轉B major key,首歌即時光明開朗晒。"},{"pid":"c6507d4d4a9d41c8c3e20940b4919f10e899ba8d","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c770b8067bb51539c268faf5b07d92d233ef1c","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"745d9198f61391a20b1ef5d7a09adf469a09b04a","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a054fa1fc0f8e9248dac41987a1f1584044c2d","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咁理解：第一part嘅間奏loop G# - C#m係開始舖定路由G# major key轉去G# minor key（or B major key).  到第二part E F# D#m G#m 就正式轉了B major key嘅4536，之後就4-5，最後一個6major（G#) chord好光明咁轉返去G# major key."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"呢個係轉調揀轉咩調既tricks<br />\n<br />\n多數揀轉升3個半度既major既話，就可以將高左3個半度既major既relative minor既root同你原本個調一樣，然後用一個cadence就可以輕易番到去原本個key（eg. Blue Bossa 第9小節開始係升3個半度，之後升番一個chord個root就可以番番原本個key）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得由一個major key轉去佢parallel minor key,似轉mode多過轉調，成件事沉晒，跟住轉返parallel major,件事又升番起晒。<br />\n<br />\n印象中AGA首Tonight 都係咁，不過倒轉：段verse先用B minor key, 製造柔情含蓄感覺，去到chorus就轉B major key,首歌即時光明開朗晒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"轉mode其實都算係轉調，因為新mode數番佢個parent scale都係唔同左。<br />\n<br />\nC Ionian -&gt; C Lydian<br />\n<br />\n即係 C Ionian -&gt; G Ionian. <br />\nC變調去G<br />\n<br />\nAGA等我聽多幾隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面岩岩出咗chord果隻Ted Lo編，好多substitution同變調<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好chur"},{"pid":"91bd7fea2c593cc46bd93d89f85e01841a1d1d78","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6507d4d4a9d41c8c3e20940b4919f10e899ba8d","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"disl