arallel major,件事又升番起晒。<br />\n<br />\n印象中AGA首Tonight 都係咁，不過倒轉：段verse先用B minor key, 製造柔情含蓄感覺，去到chorus就轉B major key,首歌即時光明開朗晒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"轉mode其實都算係轉調，因為新mode數番佢個parent scale都係唔同左。<br />\n<br />\nC Ionian -&gt; C Lydian<br />\n<br />\n即係 C Ionian -&gt; G Ionian. <br />\nC變調去G<br />\n<br />\nAGA等我聽多幾隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面岩岩出咗chord果隻Ted Lo編，好多substitution同變調<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好chur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"明白數學上轉mode都係轉調，不過我記音樂習慣會諗吓當中意思和感覺，睇吓有冇association 咁會易記啲。<br />\n<br />\n我當首歌係轉mode，一來我係有一份感受係度。記C轉去G唔知有咩意義；但C Ionian 去C Lydian 我一睇都會feel到件事係走緊去光明。<br />\n<br />\n二來理解來源調和目的調嘅關係（如parallel),件事易記過數字（雖然習慣嘅話「3個半度」這個數值都唔難記。）<br />\n<br />\n這是我的分法分享下。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"我淨係記1個半度，2個半度，3個半度同5th<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過記名係方便label個感覺又真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7681f6d33deb903bc20648a148eb4a28bd9bc0f9","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce5c952c371e257fa143b7d6fe3493a13505b2d","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91bd7fea2c593cc46bd93d89f85e01841a1d1d78","tid":2499411,"uid":252937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6507d4d4a9d41c8c3e20940b4919f10e899ba8d","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"轉mode其實都算係轉調，因為新mode數番佢個parent scale都係唔同左。<br />\n<br />\nC Ionian -&gt; C Lydian<br />\n<br />\n即係 C Ionian -&gt; G Ionian. <br />\nC變調去G<br />\n<br />\nAGA等我聽多幾隻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面岩岩出咗chord果隻Ted Lo編，好多substitution同變調<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好chur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"明白數學上轉mode都係轉調，不過我記音樂習慣會諗吓當中意思和感覺，睇吓有冇association 咁會易記啲。<