":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1314f1fdad09714bb8217593a8349182d0ecbee0","tid":2499411,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37e8e9e2ff3628a73f22c11846c4ec5a366c9bf3","tid":2499411,"uid":173515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1b16d9dca4d0ddf1759927d8792b069cb74cde","tid":2499411,"uid":236608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢想請教下<br />\n有人話作曲最好寫chord先？想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係寫咗melody再配chord反而更match咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"個人認為想邊樣凸出就寫邊樣先<br />\n利申：行內人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"各有好壞<br />\n1. chord先 : 會預先畫左框架<br />\n好處係易作左 因為已經有齊骨架, 已經有齊個feel<br />\n壞處: 你唔會諗到跳出框架既旋律<br />\n<br />\n2. 旋律優先<br />\n好處: 冇框架, 可以試到唔同得意既野<br />\n壞處: 如果你唔熟chord既聲, 個旋律可能會冇方向感,<br />\n<br />\n*用琴作曲, 如果練到夠熟晒d chord <br />\n其實左手係會自動補位彈岩既chord, 某程度上係旋律 &amp; chord同步<br />\n亦唔洗事先安排chord"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b04866ab847f7ff7608dc25a8629fc385913e8f","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d415168fbba0ecb657dd94a9b58d1aa48d547cd","tid":2499411,"uid":185866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"想請教下， 張敬軒 夜機 intro 的chord progressions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b74d503db7e9fb12444b0811ae65f526143a4e7","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d415168fbba0ecb657dd94a9b58d1aa48d547cd","tid":2499411,"uid":185866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"想請教下， 張敬軒 夜機 intro 的chord progressions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"收工有時間我寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不便之處敬請見諒"},{"pid":"769bc4f2e430071246f7653bb997ce0001f467a6","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"推住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863e7d0ecd4764e3b89aa873783a9058f1af280e","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d415168fbba0ecb657dd94a9b58d1aa48d547cd","tid":2499411,"uid":185866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"想請教下， 張敬軒 夜機 intro 的chord progressions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"遲左sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/26/uU29cm.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F26%2FuU29cm.jpeg&h=031dcd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/26/Z2NLwS.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F26%2FZ2NLwS.jpeg&h=8deed549&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e9d45b5318ea99a5a486a6944316c9dee6e84d6","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"C harmonic minor<br />\n<br />\n先寫簡易版解釋：<br />\n8個小節之中，頭尾2個chord，Cm - G係 i - V。G major既第3度B，係C的第7度，而唔係b7th，所以C minor之中、出現B（第7度），就係harmonic minor唔係natural minor<br />\n<br />\n正常以C作為 I chord，一個完整cadence 既根音係 D - G - C，D係G第5度，G係C第5度，一路以前者係後者第5度既方法下降。Harmonic minor個跌法就必然係G跌Cm，但D佢就用番major，G的secondary dominant，係為左產生呢種聲音而出現<br />\n<br />\nDb就係G既替代，tritone substitution<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以解釋，但怕太複雜變左好似上個post咁寫寫下hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後段人唱係fly me to the moon接近exact一樣，然後加上某d 過渡同替代，好似仲值得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e32a0431f02c39d382c1222f3b92c2121b8fc4d","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbbe4cfb46672431011bd7e7bd53fcc492a66a9","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ae104424162e174105031d1a5a418a94ac1e9","tid":2499411,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6191861f250b553b22694d7a837e339b7b26df7e","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e6e443bca2ac7019706a5b8c6e8a47d9c3e3deb","tid":2499411,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31aea876404c2db320e4e76d3a8e0e7b52f2c216","tid":2499411,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"要去到咩程度先聽到哂呢首既chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O06BmbcLL9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO06BmbcLL9E&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9e2b0a2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O06BmbcLL9E</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"用開software 爆，唔聽。不過大致上一聽會有感覺知係邊類。<br />\n聽唔聽到唔係好重要，比人知個走向，都做唔到咩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/22/imQwbk.jpeg\" dat