" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e32e22c9642051f811535874512e23f5e438b61","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02fc611f6ce10c24705cc07ca1338342240852b7","tid":2499411,"uid":185866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"863e7d0ecd4764e3b89aa873783a9058f1af280e","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d415168fbba0ecb657dd94a9b58d1aa48d547cd","tid":2499411,"uid":185866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"想請教下， 張敬軒 夜機 intro 的chord progressions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"遲左sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/26/uU29cm.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F26%2FuU29cm.jpeg&h=031dcd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/26/Z2NLwS.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F26%2FZ2NLwS.jpeg&h=8deed549&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:48:54.000Z","msg":"真心多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />譜寫得好靚！<br />\n<br />\n首歌我都執左好耐，執唔到中間啲音，頭6個bars 都係C bass 黎， 聽落唔係D同Db  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩唔明隨便問"}],"pinned":{"pid":"419c3557c02d534a3916c96a9b295258d0f3c941","tid":2499411,"uid":56674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"期間限定<br />\n細佬我將會再次回饋連登，舉行每星期一至兩次的<span class=\"gold\"><strong>義教</strong></span>連登巴絲結他課堂。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n－適合新手／卡樽頸已久的連登結他巴絲<br />\n－電／木結他皆可<br />\n－任何風格（我識答既就答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n－因為以前做過幾次都有放飛機既人，所以每星期只有固定兩日可選（響細佬我平時教班既節數之間或之後）<br />\n－每人可以黎最多1次<br />\n－響葵興，我的教室<br />\n－土地問題，所以每次最多1對1或1對2<br />\n－自攜結他同彈過既譜／notes<br />\n－由即日起可以報名，完結時間另行通知<br />\n－時段：<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>星期三－6pm 7pm 8pm<br />\n星期六－3pm 4pm<br />\n星期日－10am 11am</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概會講既內容：<br />\n1. 流行結他（即係普通彈唱）－中階<br />\n－點樣可以無perfect pitch，用結他指板可以搵到一首歌既key<br />\n－點樣可以執到譜／chord／識得分網上簡譜執得岩唔岩<br />\n－點樣可以彈得似原本果首歌多一啲<br />\n－掃法／勾法變化<br />\n－結他編曲編chord<br />\n－知道歌係點寫出黎<br />\n－更多內容未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n2. Blues（電結他soloing）<br />\n－基本shuffle blues soloing方法：用arpeggios/chord tone，而非pentatonics<br />\n－基本 12 bar blues comping，minor blues同shuffle blues<br />\n－大師風格剖析簡介，主要3 Kings，Jimi，Clapton，SRV<br />\n－Playing sometimes outside，如何更改12-bar blues progression內的chord產生新的outside soloing line<br />\n－standard licks and runs in both major/minor pentatonic scale<br />\n－點樣調教amp既EQ／結他上的pot value／用咩effect去拎到一個標準tone<br />\n<br />\n3. Jazz Guitar<br />\n－練習Routine：於固定把位上將chord shapes/arpeggios 沿circle of Vth彈奏<br />\n－Comping：隨住fake book上的chord將一隻jazz standard完整comp出（用chord fragment同特定rhythm有脈絡地一個接一個彈出）<br />\n－分析chord progression in any jazz standards：響任何的standard上solo或comp前都必需要做的一步<br />\n－正確基本3大modes：Ionian，Dorian，Mixolydian<br />\n－ii - V - I 於 bebop/jazz guitar soloing的標準彈奏方法／chord擺法<br />\n－太多未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以直接聯絡我：<a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8036fc24\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a>"}}